{"tid":573568,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[又到轉會時間] uTorrent軟體漏洞可使惡意網站取得電腦控制權、竊取資料","createTime":"2018-02-26T14:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T05:00:58.000Z","uid":1402,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dd2d1b8c129f8e067aeef4b67f6d352951eea630","tid":573568,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T14:49:10.000Z","msg":"竟然冇人講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n擁有數百萬用戶的BitTorrent用戶端軟體uTorrent Windows及Web兩個版本被發現有重大漏洞，可能讓攻擊者得以執行遠端程式碼或拷走用戶下載的檔案。<br />\n<br />\n兩項漏洞是由Google Project Zero安全研究人員Tarvis Ormandy揭露並通報BitTorrent。BitTorrent軟體包括uTorrent旨在讓用戶在開放網路上共享及存取檔案。uTorrent會在用戶電腦上架一台伺服器，利用BitTorrent協定進行檔案分享。<br />\n<br />\nOrmandy指出，uTorrent的Windows及Web版分別是在port 10000及19575建立HTTP RPC伺服器,,。任何網站只要用XMLHTTPRequest()指令，就可以開採這些伺服器。<br />\n<br />\n他在uTorrent Web及Windows兩個版本發現的設計瑕疵，前者曝露uTorrent服務的認證密鑰、電腦紀錄檔、設定等其他機密，讓網站可接管uTorrent服務，後者則讓任何網站得以讀取及複製用戶下載的檔案，或者載入惡意程式到Windows啟動資料夾，等下次電腦重新開機時自動執行，進行任何想做的事。<br />\n<br />\nProject Zero將這兩項漏洞定為重大風險，過程中一度發生BitTorrent修補不完整，使研究人員急著在90天寬限期屆滿之前聯絡BitTorrent。幸而現在修復版uTorrent 3.5.3.44352版已開放下載。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/121402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com.tw%2Fnews%2F121402&d=S2%2FSHC2DKKQvHz6ht6PKwFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=516c893e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/121402</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">It turns out that BitTorrent just made added an additional token to uTorrent Web, and was still vulnerable to the same attack.</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">the issue remains unsolved.</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nref: <a href=\"https://bugs.chromium.org/p/project-zero/issues/detail?id=1524#c10\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbugs.chromium.org%2Fp%2Fproject-zero%2Fissues%2Fdetail%3Fid%3D1524%23c10&d=S2%2FSHC2DKKQvHz6ht6PKwFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=73d11de7\" target=\"_blank\">https://bugs.chromium.org/p/project-zero/issues/detail?id=1524#c10</a>"},{"pid":"2bdf95867ad0f1c796042f696aa32f3b9e41220b","tid":573568,"uid":94820,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T14:50:48.000Z","msg":"仲有人用uTorrent?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18526f424f79401acca6d16e8ada9b5707267a10","tid":573568,"uid":80514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T14:51:44.000Z","msg":"In aria2, we trust"},{"pid":"06a780b52aabfaa717be480516e27ed713c225de","tid":573568,"uid":32661,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2bdf95867ad0f1c796042f696aa32f3b9e41220b","tid":573568,"uid":94820,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T14:50:48.000Z","msg":"仲有人用uTorrent?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T14:52:30.000Z","msg":"Me <br />\n因為transmission 連唔到https tracker 個bug仲未fix <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89baf454723c97420a0cfeb2fa231c9b576bb10d","tid":573568,"uid":30148,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T14:52:33.000Z","msg":"husky幾時轉會迅雷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb8ebd9f5a074527690cf76784a770dda392223","tid":573568,"uid":33057,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T14:52:49.000Z","msg":"轉左qb好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e836671b2106ddcd2b3227cc1c0302351a3750fa","tid":573568,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89baf454723c97420a0cfeb2fa231c9b576bb10d","tid":573568,"uid":30148,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T14:52:33.000Z","msg":"husky幾時轉會迅雷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T14:54:14.000Z","msg":"用緊唔通話你知咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif